{"article_id":"v1y3NQktTaDFDKaN","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"FBI director James Comey on Wednesday described Russia as \" the greatest threat \" to US democracy ,","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"but defended his decision to keep secret an investigation into the Trump campaign ' s links to Moscow","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"despite revealing details of an inquiry into Hillary Clinton ' s handling of classified emails .","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"Hillary Clinton :","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"I 'm to blame for election loss","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"but outside interference cost me","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"Read more","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"Giving evidence to a hearing of the Senate judiciary committee ,","depth":4},{"id":8,"text":"Comey offered his most extensive explanation to date of the thinking behind his different approaches to the two investigations .","depth":4},{"id":9,"text":"Clinton claimed on Tuesday","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"that Comey ' s 28 October letter to leading members of Congress about new emails","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"that had been found","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"damaged voter perceptions of her","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"and cost her the election .","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"\" If the election had been on 27 October ,","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"I would be your president , \"","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"the former Democratic presidential candidate said .","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"The discovery of the emails ultimately made no difference to the FBI decision","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"not to press charges over the use of the private server .","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"Asked about Clinton ' s claim","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"that his letter could have swung the vote ,","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"Comey said :","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"\" This was terrible .","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"It makes me mildly nauseous to think","depth":11},{"id":24,"text":"we might have had some impact on the election .","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"But honestly , I wouldn ' t change the decision . \"","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"The FBI director said","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"that the discovery in October of a new batch classified emails put him in a near impossible dilemma .","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"He said","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"he had to make a choice between \" speak or conceal \" :","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"to speak would have been \" really bad \" ,","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"he said ;","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"to conceal would have been \" catastrophic \" .","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"So he chose to speak out .","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"\" One of my junior lawyers asked me :","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"should you consider","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"what you do might help elect Trump as president ?","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"I said :","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"not for a moment , \"","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"Comey said ,","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"arguing","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"that political considerations should never be a factor in such decisions .","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"Trump responded to Clinton ' s comments on Tuesday with a tweet","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"claiming :","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"\" FBI Director Comey was the best thing","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"that ever happened to Hillary Clinton","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"in that he gave her a free pass for many bad deeds ! \"","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"- an apparent reference to the bureau ' s finding","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"that there was nothing","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"to prosecute in the emails case .","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"Asked about the criticism on Wednesday ,","depth":6},{"id":51,"text":"the White House spokesman , Sean Spicer , told journalists :","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"\" The president has confidence in the director . \"","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"He was asked repeatedly about the contrast between his decision","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"to break silence on the Clinton email case","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"while concealing the existence of a counter-intelligence investigation into the Trump campaign ' s contacts with Russian officials during the election .","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"Comey said","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"that","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"when he first spoke about the Clinton case , in July 2016 ,","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"he did so","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"because the investigation had been closed ,","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"no charges had been made ,","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"and he felt","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"that","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"if the Department of Justice in the Obama administration made the announcement","depth":13},{"id":65,"text":"it would lose credibility .","depth":13},{"id":66,"text":"The discovery of more emails in October might have changed that decision","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"and represented an important development ,","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"he added .","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"The Trump-Russia counter-intelligence investigation ,","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"he argued ,","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"was highly classified","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"and was in its \" very early stages \" by the time of the election .","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"UK was given details of alleged contacts between Trump campaign and Moscow","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"Read more","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"He confirmed","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"that the inquiry was continuing ,","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"and agreed","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"when asked whether it was \" fair to say","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"that Russia is still involved in American politics \" .","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"He went further ,","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"describing Russia as \" the greatest threat of any nation on earth ,","depth":12},{"id":82,"text":"given their intention and their capability \"","depth":12},{"id":83,"text":"to US democracy .","depth":11},{"id":84,"text":"Asked about Comey ' s claim","depth":8},{"id":85,"text":"that the Russian government is still involved in US politics ,","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"Spicer replied :","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"\" I think","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"that ' s the view of the FBI .","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"We rely on them and the rest of the intelligence community to provide the president with updates on what they ' re learning . \"","depth":8},{"id":90,"text":"At his hearing , Comey was peppered with questions about leaks about FBI investigations ,","depth":4},{"id":91,"text":"and repeatedly stated","depth":5},{"id":92,"text":"he could neither confirm or deny .","depth":5},{"id":93,"text":"He made one exception , however .","depth":4},{"id":94,"text":"Asked about contacts between FBI staff and Rudy Giuliani , a former New York mayor and current Trump aide ,","depth":6},{"id":95,"text":"he said :","depth":6},{"id":96,"text":"\" I don ' t know yet ,","depth":6},{"id":97,"text":"but it ' s a matter","depth":7},{"id":98,"text":"I ' m very , very interested in . \"","depth":7},{"id":99,"text":"Comey described in detail the process","depth":6},{"id":100,"text":"of discovering Clinton ' s emails on the laptop of Anthony Weiner , the estranged husband of top Clinton aide Huma Abedin .","depth":6},{"id":101,"text":"He said","depth":7},{"id":102,"text":"that \" somehow \" Clinton ' s emails \" were being forwarded to Anthony Weiner ,","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"including classified information ,","depth":9},{"id":104,"text":"by her assistant Huma Abedin \" .","depth":8},{"id":105,"text":"Weiner was being investigated over an alleged online relationship with a teenage girl .","depth":6},{"id":106,"text":"Republican Chuck Grassley , the chairman of the committee , said","depth":6},{"id":107,"text":"that the public ' s faith in the bureau had been tested lately .","depth":6},{"id":108,"text":"Grassley is pressing for answers about the FBI ' s investigation into potential coordination between the Trump campaign and Russia .","depth":6},{"id":109,"text":"Comey disclosed the existence of that investigation","depth":7},{"id":110,"text":"when he testified at a congressional hearing in March .","depth":7},{"id":111,"text":"Comey also mounted a strong defence of section 702 of the Fisa Amendments Act of 2008 ,","depth":5},{"id":112,"text":"which allows the NSA to use the Prism program","depth":6},{"id":113,"text":"to collect internet communications .","depth":6},{"id":114,"text":"And he claimed","depth":5},{"id":115,"text":"that half the FBI ' s work was now affected by encryption on users ' phones or other devices .","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":231,"left":205,"right":230,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":205,"left":124,"right":204,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":124,"left":122,"right":123,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":122,"left":118,"right":121,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":118,"left":0,"right":117,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":117,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":121,"left":120,"right":6,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":120,"left":3,"right":119,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":119,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":123,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":204,"left":156,"right":203,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":156,"left":140,"right":155,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":140,"left":131,"right":139,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":131,"left":128,"right":130,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":128,"left":9,"right":127,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":127,"left":125,"right":126,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":125,"left":10,"right":11,"rel